       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI10403         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV1040.
       COPY COCV1041.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY TGCL1000.
       COPY TGCL2000.
       COPY TGCK0002.
      *
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 WS-PROGNAME  PIC X(08) VALUE 'COI10403'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-CIDEMP        PIC X(05) VALUE 'CO507'.
           05 CON-CTABELA-NIDPROJECTO   PIC X(05) VALUE 'CO513'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-CTABELA                   PIC X(05) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CCOD                      PIC X(40) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-C2COD                     PIC X(40) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-NUMERICO                  PIC 9(03).
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-NUMERICO.
              10 WS-CODIGO                 PIC X(03).
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI10403         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      *
           MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV1040-MSG.
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV1041-MSG.
      *    MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT   TO COCV1041-MSG.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.
      *
           MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2100-VAL-CAMPOS
                 THRU 2100-VAL-CAMPOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-VAL-CAMPOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-VAL-CAMPOS.
      *
           MOVE '2100-VAL-CAMPOS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE 'COCV1040-CIDEMP     '    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  COCV1040-CIDEMP          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'COCV1041-CIDEMP     '    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE  COCV1041-CIDEMP          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV1040-CIDEMP       NOT EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE CON-CTABELA-CIDEMP
                 TO WS-CTABELA
               MOVE COCV1040-CIDEMP
                 TO WS-CCOD
               MOVE SPACES
                 TO WS-C2COD
               PERFORM 2300-VAL-TAB-OUTRA
                  THRU 2300-VAL-TAB-OUTRA-EXIT
               IF NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                  MOVE TGCL1000-CCOD-S
                    TO COCV1041-CIDEMP-S
                  MOVE TGCL1000-CCOD-CAPLIC
                    TO COCV1041-CIDEMP-CAPLIC
                  MOVE TGCL1000-CCOD-MSG
                    TO COCV1041-CIDEMP-MSG
                  MOVE TGCL1000-GDESC
                    TO COCV1041-XDESCCIDEMP
               ELSE
                  MOVE TGCL1000-GDESC
                    TO COCV1040-XDESCCIDEMP
               END-IF
           END-IF.

